eapons.  I am currently swapping between a Servant's Blade, (11/30 5 Dex Stam and HP) Centi Shortsword (12/25 few stats, unsure what ATM) and my Ykesa War club (9/24 Procs 75 DD)<br>I mainly run with Centi main, Yak offhand, and I am unsure if this is my most effective combo.  I find the sweet delay holds aggro when I want to, or helps Taunt work better, but it seems, (again, not sure) that the Servant Blade main and Centi offhand seems to have a bit better damage output.<br><br>Opinions are welcome, and the more info provided the better.  I can easily solo most deep blues, (4-5 in a row if animals lol) and I would like to make shorter work of non-animals as the healing downtime is a pain and Kiting is too slow. <p><center><br> With love comes purpose, commitment and dedication.<br>With these, come ferocity and courage.<br>With these, success is only a matter of time.<br><img src="http://www.members.accesswave.ca/~banditobru/falsig69.jpg"<br><br>44th Season Ranger of Tunare<br>Guild Chronicler & Proud Officer<br>Coalition of Power<br>Husband and Protector of Shylee Whipawill<br>"Facts will change, depending on who is telling the tale, but the truth will always remain the same."<br>*The Chronicler's notes* <br> <br><a href=http://www.accesswave.ca/~falwith>Falwith's Glade</a><br><a href="mailto:falwith@hotmail.com">Mail me</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ualadinsaneuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>aladinsaneuk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/2/02 2:24:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=567.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.petedean.btinternet.co.uk/aladstyle.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top