t a Green Jade Broadsword, Crystaline Short sword, hell even a Lamentation.  Since Luclin came out all the prices on these have dropped big time, specially the Lam.  You could get lucky and get a lam for 3k, CSS for 2k, GJB for about 2k also.  Yak war club is decent for getting 1hb up, but when it procs could cause a problem from 45 to 51 when you get Jolt.   <p><img SRC="http://www.kerinakreation.com/images/sigs/brenilpic.jpg"></br>Brenil O'Soreru</br>56th Defiler & Defender of Kataki O'Soreru</br></br>Acception Heavonsent</br>55th Outrider & Protector of Patchee Heavonsent</br><br><br>"....Excuse me, while I...whip this out..."</br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufalwith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Falwith</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.members.accesswave.ca/~falwith/Screenshots/tinypic.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/3/02 5:46:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=567.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.accesswave.ca/~falwith/Screenshots/face.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weapon and stat question</span><hr size=1> I should have thought to mention I have little, if any cash to play with.<br>I laugh so often at the &quot;It's only 1K&quot; and such statements that I disregard most weapons associated with those prices.  Dropping 400 P and an item for the Centi Short sword was a stretch for me, leaving me almost broke once again.<br>That said, since the 1 to 2k items seem to be common fare for suggestions, I'll ask where you guys GET the 2k to toss into weapons.  Day to day survival and paying my way, (ports, the occasional res, gems for symbols etc) seem to keep my cash extremely low.  I have had a grand total of 1600 P on h