ot lucky and won a demi drop that wasn't needed by anyone.  Bought a Hand of the Reaper and was broke again yay.  <br><br>Anyway, for anyone in their 50s able to go to Velks, Seb, Karnors, ect.  Just hang in groups get exp, and you'll eventually get something.  In Karnors, less often, in Seb at least you'll get some money items, which add up.  NGE just wtfowns for cash, not only do you get a shitload of money items, you can get diamons, blue diamonds, lamentations and other stuff off of named.  There's lots of ways to make money, just when you try too hard like with everything it's normally harder than when you're not thinking about it.  So relax go get exp in different places, and you'll get money eventually. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img SRC="http://www.kerinakreation.com/images/sigs/brenilpic.jpg"></br>Brenil O'Soreru</br>56th Defiler & Defender of Kataki O'Soreru</br></br>Acception Heavonsent</br>55th Outrider & Protector of Patchee Heavonsent</br><br><br>"....Excuse me, while I...whip this out..."</br></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.showPrevMessage?topicID=567.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.showNextMessage?topicID=567.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=567.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumranger.emailToFriend?topicID=567.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><